      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――誕生祭当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of the birthday festival",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "二代目星降る奇跡、成宮すずの誕生祭\nみなさん、楽しんでいらっしゃいますかー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The second “Starry Miracle”‚ Suzu Narumiya's Birthday Festival!\nIs everyone having fun~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.9666666905,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2200.0000079,
          "startTime": 8.1666666984
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.5122213283
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "星見市が生んだプリンセス、すずにゃん様と\nみんなでもっともっと盛り上がっていこー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s get even more hyped up with\nHoshimi City’s princess‚ Suzunyan-sama!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.0333324033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.5823589245
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "今日は……とってもおめでたい日……\n国民の祝日になっても、おかしくない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today… is a very auspicious day…\nIt wouldn’t be strange even if it were a national holiday!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.2666673897,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10999.999308700002,
          "startTime": 34.2666666984
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.2889345724
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、ええ！　その通りですわ！\n今日この日を、成宮すず誕生記念日といたします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ yes! You’re absolutely right!\nI hereby declare today Suzu Narumiya’s birthday!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.8189349412,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.3093178351
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "ライブパートの終わりに、ファンのみんなと\n撮った記念写真……家宝にする……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The commemorative photo we took with all the fans at the end of\nthe live part… I’m going to treasure it as a family heirloom…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.2666653871,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.1669371525
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "ぜひ、後世に語り継いでくださいまし！\n二代目星降るきしぇきですから！　……あっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Be sure to pass it down for generations to come!\nAfter all‚ I’m the second “Starry Miricle”! …Ah.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.6146468085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.0402704476
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "噛み噛みすずにゃん様も可愛い～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even when she’s stumbling over her words‚ Suzunyan-sama is so cute~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.9666653871,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.7870255549
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "からかわないでくださいまし！\nそれより、クイズ大会は楽しめましたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t tease me!\nSo‚ did you enjoy the quiz show?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.5503813667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.4108803192
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃん様に関する問題、面白かったー！\n雫ちゃん全問正解おめでとう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The quiz about Suzunyan-sama was fun~!\nCongratulations to Shizuku for getting every question right!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.633329765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.7776846964
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "……ぶい\nすずちゃん様のことなら、任せて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…V sign\nIf it’s about Suzuchan-sama‚ leave it to me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.8666671674,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.281020236
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　すずにゃん様！　星見プロのみんなから\n沢山のプレゼントが届いてるみたいだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! Suzunyan-sama! It looks like Hoshimi Prods members\nsent a bunch of presents!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.1000005007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "象は呼べなかったけど、クマなら……ある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We couldn’t get an elephant‚ but we do have… Winnie the Pooh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1501089811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "こんなにもらっていいんですの！？\n全部、私に……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you sure I can accept all of this!?\nAll of it… for me…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.9921927378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよ！　ぜーんぶすずにゃん様へのプレゼント！\nそれじゃあ、雫ちゃん、いくよ！　せーのっ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right! It’s all for Suzu-nyan-sama!\nAlright‚ Shizuku‚ let’s do it! Ready… set…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.7999943973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "すずにゃん様、お誕生日、おめでと～～～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Happy birthday‚ Suzunyan-sama!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.7683333319,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3431.664371400004,
          "startTime": 106.1999977033
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、雫……っ！　そしてファンのみなさん……っ\n心より感謝を申し上げます……私は、幸せ者ですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei‚ Shizuku…! And all of you fans…!\nI thank you all from the bottom of my heart… I’m so blessed!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.1756133642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "今日は……本当に……っ\n最高の誕生日ですわ～～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today… is truly…\nthe best birthday ever!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.275612347,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1209.061510799998,
          "startTime": 128.4846738578
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.7727796954
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.2089466976
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "みなさんからの祝福、今日は沢山受け取りました\nこの勢いで、私……成宮すずは――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve received so many blessings from everyone today.\nWith this momentum‚ I… Suzu Narumiya will――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.2089466976,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6424.384338999999,
          "startTime": 144.6333310366
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.3213682891
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルの天下を取りますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "conquer the idol world!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.3213682891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.5280287665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "……でも今日で、取ったも同然……\nすでに、天下はすずにゃん様の手にあり……です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But it’s as good as conquered today…\nThe world is already in Suzunyan-sama’s hands…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.3666539432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.6798654796
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、別の目標が必要かも？\nすずにゃん様、世界一のアイドルに！　ってどうかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe we need a different goal then?\nHow about “Suzunyan-sama‚ the world’s best idol!” ?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.1333206099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.0684326729
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "素晴らしいですわ！\n目標は大きいほどいいのです。それでは――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wonderful!\nThe bigger the goal‚ the better. Well then――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.0739704696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 169.6103600741
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
