      "text": "お誕生日に……お姫様気分を味わってほしくて\nでも芽衣達、ちょっとやり過ぎちゃったかも。ごめんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We wanted you to feel like a princess on your birthday…\nbut maybe we went a little overboard‚ Mei. We’re sorry.",
