      "text": "急な告白……でも、私も同じ……隣でいろんな\nすずちゃんを見れたから、もっと好きになった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A sudden confession… But I feel the same way… Being by your side and seeing\ndifferent sides of you‚ Suzu-chan‚ made me like you more…",
