      "text": "ファンのみんなを考えて、丁寧に企画してるとこ、とか\nもちろん、上機嫌で喜んでるとこ、とかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The way you carefully planned everything with the fans in mind‚ and…\nOf course‚ how happy and cheerful you were…",
        "id": ""
