      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "夜遅くまで準備を頑張ってたところも\n褒めたら、意外と照れ屋さんになっちゃうところも！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The way you worked hard preparing until late at night…\nand how shy you get when you’re praised…!",
